    <item>
      <title>拜登推动地热能源促进人工智能发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/biden-to-push-geothermal-as-key-energy-source-for-ai-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，总统乔·拜登的政府计划简化地热能开发许可，作为一项更广泛的行政命令的一部分，以加强人工智能数据中心的基础设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/biden-to-push-geothermal-as-key-energy-source-for-ai-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 01:30:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia CEO 认为量子计算应用还需要几年时间，股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/quantum-computing-stocks-drop-as-nvidia-ceo-sees-use-years-away</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英伟达公司首席执行官黄仁勋表示“非常有用的”量子计算机可能还需要几十年的时间后，IonQ Inc. 和其他与量子计算相关的公司的股价在周二的盘后交易中暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/quantum-computing-stocks-drop-as-nvidia-ceo-sees-use-years-away</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 00:53:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达传闻抵消利润损失后，三星股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/samsung-profit-disappoints-after-ai-chip-missteps-hurt-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司创始人黄仁勋表示，他相信三星电子有能力解决其最高端内存的技术问题，这抵消了令人失望的季度业绩影响。此后，三星电子股价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/samsung-profit-disappoints-after-ai-chip-missteps-hurt-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 23:38:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
